comments.body:
@iSazonov  I haven't, but thanks for the input.
I have seen many other modules out there, like: PoshRSJob & Invoke-Parallel.

Invoke-Command already has a -ThrottleLimit parameter, and works well with remote execution. But why not enable it for local execution? Even if it uses jobs internally, or some other mechanism. Why make the user download an external module?
